<i>noun</i>: 확인 [화긴], 증명 [증명], 검증 [검ː증] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>확인 [화긴]</dt><br>
<dd>check; affirmation; confirmation; verification</dd><br>
<dd>틀림없이 그러한지를 알아보거나 인정함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of finding out if something is true or admitting that it is true.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>증명 [증명]</dt><br>
<dd>1. verification; testification</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 사건이나 내용이나 판단이 진실인지 아닌지를 증거를 들어서 밝힘.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of establishing that an event, some certain content, or a decision is true by presenting proof.</dd><br>
<dd>2. paper; certificate</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 사실이 진실임을 밝히는 문서.</dd><br>
<dd>A document showing that a fact is true.</dd><br>
<dd>3. proving</dd><br>
<dd>수학이나 논리학에서, 어떤 명제나 판단이 진실인지 아닌지를 근본 원리로부터 이끌어 내어 밝힘.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of demonstrating that a proposition or judgment is true by using fundamental principles, in mathematics or logic.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>검증 [검ː증]</dt><br>
<dd>1. verification; inspection</dd><br>
<dd>검사하여 사실임을 증명함.</dd><br>
<dd>Inspecting and proving that something is true.</dd><br>
<dd>2. verification of a piece of evidence</dd><br>
<dd>법관이나 수사관이 증거를 조사하는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>A judicial officer or investigator examining evidence.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>